import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Grid,
  TextField
} from '@material-ui/core';
import ListStudent from '../component/Class/ListStudent';
import ListTeacher from '../component/Class/ListTeacher';
import Student from '../data/studentdb';

const AddClass = () => (
  <>
    <Helmet>
      <title>AddClass</title>
    </Helmet>
    <Box
      sx={{
        backgroundColor: 'background.default',
        minHeight: '100%',
        py: 3
      }}
    >

      

      <Container maxWidth={false}>

        <Grid
          container
          spacing={6}
        >
          <Grid item lg={3}>
          <TextField required id="standard-required" label="Required" defaultValue="CLassName" />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item lg={3}>
          <TextField required id="standard-required" label="Required" defaultValue="Room" />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item lg={3}>
          <TextField required id="standard-required" label="Required" defaultValue="Credits" />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item lg={3}>
          <TextField required id="standard-required" label="Required" defaultValue="Date_Start" />
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid
            item
            lg={6}
          >
            <ListStudent student={Student}/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid
            item
            lg={6}
          >
            <ListTeacher teacher={Student}/>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  </>
);

export default AddClass;
